    "chemicalDescription": [
      "Tripeptide-46 Hexapeptide-40 Decapeptide-27 Oligopeptide-91 Dipeptide-19 sh-Polypeptide-60 Tetrapeptide-48 is a single chain synthetic fusion peptide, produced by fermentation in  E. coli.  The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from Tripeptide-46, Hexapeptide-40, Decapeptide-27, Oligopeptide-91, Dipeptide-19, sh-Polypeptide-60 and Tetrapeptide-48. The fusion peptide contains 140 amino acids and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids"
